Sandclock Engine Codestyle

Class Names
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
	- Name the class after what it is. 
	- Compound names of no more than two words.
	- First character in a name is upper case.
	- Use upper case letters as word separators, lower case for the rest of a word.
	- No underbars ('_')

Method and Function Names
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
	- The name should make clear what it does: CheckForErrors() instead of ErrorCheck(), DumpDataToFile() instead of DataFile().
	- Use of prefixes like Is/Get/Set.
	- First character in a name is upper case.
	- Use upper case letters as word separators, lower case for the rest of a word.
	- No underbars ('_')
	
Enum Names
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
	-Enum labels should be all caps with '_' separators.

Global Constants
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
	-Global constants should be all caps with '_' separators.

Variable Names
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
	- The first character should be lower case.
	- All word beginnings after the first letter should be upper case as with class names.
	
Brace Policy
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
	- Brace under and inline with keywords

Identation/Tab Policy
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
	-Identation = 4
	-Tab = 4
